In a skillet, over medium-high heat, add butter, then brown the beef until golden brown. Add onions and mushrooms, and cook for another 2 to 3 minutes, or until onions are translucent. Stir in broccoli, UNCLE BEN'S(R) Flavor Infusions Garlic & Butter Rice, and water. Bring to boil, then reduce to medium heat and simmer covered for 15 minutes or until water is absorbed.